SUMMARY:✨ Road Trip to Niagara Falls: Jeffrey Osborne & Will Downing Liv
 e ✨ $50 total
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Movies & Social Group - Celebrating 14 Years!\n✨ **R
 oad Trip to Niagara Falls: Jeffrey Osborne & Will Downing Live** ✨\n**Sa
 turday\, February 28**\nJoin us for a fun winter road trip to **Niagara Fa
 lls** for a great night of live R&B entertainment featuring **Jeffrey Osbo
 rne & Will Downing** at the **OLG Stage at Fallsview Casino**. A perfect S
 aturday night getaway with music\, laughs\, and good company.\n\n[Read mor
 e about the show here](https://fallsviewcasinoresort.com/events-and-promot
 ions/schedule-of-events/jeffrey-osborne-will-downing.html)\n\n***\n\n### 
 🕒 Schedule\n\n* **4:00 PM** – Depart Toronto\n📍 *Pickup: outside C
 hristie Station*\n* **Early Evening** – Possible sightseeing or free tim
 e in Niagara Falls *(traffic permitting)*\n* **7:30 PM** – Showtime at t
 he **OLG Stage at Fallsview Casino**\n* **\\~12:00 AM (Midnight)** – App
 roximate return to Toronto\n\n***\n\n### 🎤 About the Venue: OLG Stage\n
 \nThe **OLG Stage at Fallsview Casino** is a modern\, state-of-the-art con
 cert venue in the heart of the Fallsview entertainment district.\n**Venue 
 highlights:**\n\n* 🎶 Excellent sound and acoustics\n* 👀 Great sightl
 ines throughout the theatre\n* 🪑 Comfortable seating with generous legr
 oom\n* 🍹 Bars and concessions on site\n* 📍 Connected to Fallsview Ca
 sino and close to restaurants and attractions\n\nIt’s one of Ontario’s
  premier venues and a fantastic place to enjoy live performances.\n\n***\n
 \n### 🚗 Transportation\n\nWe’ll be travelling together in a **Kia Sou
 l** equipped with:\n\n* ❄️ **Winter tires**\n* 📻 **SiriusXM satelli
 te radio**\n\nSafe\, comfortable\, and perfect for a cozy winter road trip
 .\n\n***\n\n### 💵 Cost & Payment\n\n* **$50 per person** *(includes con
 cert ticket + round-trip transportation)*\n* **Must eTransfer $50 to nicol
 asbello@yahoo.com to lock in your spot**\n* Your RSVP is confirmed **only 
 after payment is received**\n\n***\n\n### ✅ Important Notes\n\n* Limited
  seats available\n* Please RSVP only if you’re **100% sure you can atten
 d**\n\n***\n\n🎉 **Great entertainment\, a top-tier venue\, and a stress
 -free road trip** — come join us for a fun Saturday night in Niagara Fal
 ls!
