SUMMARY:Niagara Falls - Cat Lovers trip by $10 roundtrip GO Train
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Movies & Social Group - Celebrating 14 Years!\nFeline 
 fancier? If yes \, this is the trip for you. We'll be visiting the Niagara
  Falls area and their [lovely cat cafe. ](https://niagarafallscatcafe.ca/)
  Limited spots available for this so sign up soon.\n\n**REMINDER - clocks 
 go forward at 2AM today so please ensure you're ready for that when planni
 ng your trip**\n\nWe will be having lunch at the cat cafe. [ Full menu her
 e](https://niagarafallscatcafe.ca/menu)\n\n**You are responsible for your 
 own food/drink bill.** The $10 only covers 1hr at the cat cafe.\n\n**You m
 ust send your cat cafe $10 fee to nicolasbello@yahoo.com when you sign up 
 for this event.**\n\nOur single-story venue was designed with accessibilit
 y in mind. There are NO steps/stairs at our Cafe and one of our two washro
 oms is accessibly sized!\n\n**Please read everything before signing up!**\
 n\n[WhatsApp for this event](https://chat.whatsapp.com/FDfbPqh5Xc3Kh39eFcQ
 WsB)\n\nFirst and foremost\, **there is lots and lots of walking on this t
 rip.** We'll walk from train station to the cat cafe\, attractions\, lunch
 \, etc. Please wear comfortable walking shoes.\n\nWe'll also \, of course\
 , have to walk back to train at end of our day. **Only sign up if you're c
 omfortable with a lot of walking.**\n\n**Cost for the GO Train Per Person:
 ** $10 round-trip with their [weekend day pass deal](https://www.gotransit
 .com/en/partners-and-promotions/weekend-passes-with-go) . **Do not buy you
 r pass until March 1**! Passes are valid for one week from purchase date.\
 n\nYou can also pay with your Presto but it will cost more than $10 for th
 e trip. Get the day pass instead.\n\n**The Day Of**:\n\n**Meetup Spot:** N
 orth side of Front St W. In front of Fairmont Royal York. Look for Nick wh
 o'll be holding Meetup signs\n\n**Meetup time:** 8:15AM and the **train WI
 LL LEAVE AT 9:04AM**. SHARP! As per GO policy now the doors will close one
  minute earlier @ 9:03AM\n\n**If you are late you miss the train\, and you
  miss the MEETUP.**\n\n**Arrival Time:** 11:25AM\n\nFrom there we have a s
 hort walk to the cats. From Noon-1PM we will have our cat cafe booking. Al
 l cats available for adoption as well.\n\n**By joining this event you're a
 greeing to come with us for the cat cafe + [lunch experience](https://niag
 arafallscatcafe.ca/menu) . You must send your cat cafe $10 fee to nicolasb
 ello@yahoo.com when you sign up for this event.**\n\nThose that would like
  to join me after \, can walk with me along the falls and enjoy the sights
 . Take photos and just chat with other members. There is a lot of other th
 ings to do at the falls.\n\n**Train Leaves:** **4pm SHARP** \\- The train 
 will leave right on time and\\\, as per GO policy now\\\, the doors will c
 lose one minute earlier at 3:59PM\\.\n\nIf you want to stay later or overn
 ight you can make your own arrangements. If you wish to return to Toronto 
 later there are trains at 7:58PM and 10PM\n\n[PDF train schedule here ](ht
 tps://assets.metrolinx.com/image/upload/v1765347924/Documents/GO/full-sche
 dules/FS20122025/TABLE01.pdf)\n\nDon't Forget to join our email list (Meet
 up does not send out emails to everyone in a group) to get our weekly news
  later about upcoming events: [http://eepurl.com/hKt76f](http://eepurl.com
 /hKt76f)\n\nNick is the organizer for this meetup. If you need to contact 
 him\, please post a message on the wall\, or email him nicolasbello@yahoo.
 com\n\n**THIS GROUP IS OPEN TO THOSE THAT WANT TO BE SOCIAL\, MAKE FRIENDS
 \, THAT ARE SINGLE OR NOT SINGLE. WE ALSO HAVE LOTS OF OTHER EVENTS LIKE\,
  MOVIES\, WALKS\, HIKES\, ARTS & CULTURE AND RESTAURANTS. WE LOVE TO SUPPO
 RT MEMEBERS TO SOCIALIZE AND TO FORM LONG LASTING FRIENDSHIPS.**\n\n**Rule
 s:** [Click Here!](https://www.meetup.com/toronto-movies-and-social-group/
 events/293241263/)\n**Getting The Best Out Of MeetUp:** [Click Here!](http
 s://www.meetup.com/toronto-movies-and-social-group/events/293241269/)\n\nD
 on't Forget to join our email list (Meetup does not send out emails to\nev
 eryone in a group) to get our weekly news later about upcoming events: [ht
 tp://eepurl.com/hKt76f](http://eepurl.com/hKt76f)\n\nFacebook group @ [htt
 p://www.facebook.com/groups/502945113062739/](http://www.facebook.com/grou
 ps/502945113062739/)
